title: Sailing in Style With Fraser CEO

description:
Raphael Sauleau, CEO of Fraser Yachts, discusses seeing strong demand for luxury boats post-pandemic.
Hosts: Carol Massar and Tim Stenovec. Producer: Paul Brennan.
